          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Help Students Repay Act</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Education to consolidate student loan repayment options for new borrowers of William D. Ford Federal Direct Loans into one simplified income-driven repayment plan. <strong></strong></p>]]></text>
